{"word":"Salt","slug":"salt","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Salt</b> Lot's wife turned into a pillar of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=19&verse=26'>Gen 19:26</a><br/> The city of Salt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=62'>Jos 15:62</a><br/> The valley of salt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=13'>2Sa 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=7'>2Ki 14:7</a><br/> Salt Sea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=3'>Gen 14:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=12'>Num 34:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=17'>Deu 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=3&verse=16'>Jos 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=3'>Jos 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=2'>Jos 15:2</a><br/> Saltpits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=36&chapter=2&verse=9'>Zep 2:9</a><br/> All animal sacrifices were required to be seasoned with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=2&verse=13'>Lev 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=9'>Ezr 6:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=43&verse=24'>Eze 43:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=49'>Mar 9:49</a><br/> Used in ratifying covenants<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=19'>Num 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=5'>2Ch 13:5</a><br/> Elisha casts salt into the pool of Jericho to purify it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=21'>2Ki 2:21</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of the saving efficacy of the church<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=5&verse=13'>Mat 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=50'>Mar 9:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=14&verse=34'>Luk 14:34</a> <br/> - Of wise conversation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=4&verse=6'>Col 4:6</a> "}]}